<span id="freeTextContainer8902513317374308361">A clever Christie with a difference. Not a who done it so much but a how done it. A bit of a crime novel in reverse like Columbo. Ah I like stories like this. A bit different and makes you think.<br/><br/>I&apos;m on a Christie mission at the moment to reread or read the titles of those classics I want to discover again. <br/><br/>There&apos;s all kinds of twists and turns here. Foreshadowing of things to come. Shadows of the past. Witchery goings on. A group of women with killing on their mind. Perhaps not the most memorabl</span>
  <span id="freeText8902513317374308361" style="display:none">A clever Christie with a difference. Not a who done it so much but a how done it. A bit of a crime novel in reverse like Columbo. Ah I like stories like this. A bit different and makes you think.<br /><br />I'm on a Christie mission at the moment to reread or read the titles of those classics I want to discover again. <br /><br />There's all kinds of twists and turns here. Foreshadowing of things to come. Shadows of the past. Witchery goings on. A group of women with killing on their mind. Perhaps not the most memorable Christie characters but there's a lot to like here.</span>
